Class NBTArrayList

  • java.lang.Object
    • lib.nbt.NBTList
      • lib.nbt.NBTArrayList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Object>, java.util.List<java.lang.Object>

    public class NBTArrayList
extends NBTList
    An extension of NBTList used to allow manipulation of the arrays contained by Array-typed tags (i.e. Byte, Int, and Long arrays).
    Author:
    Kyrillos Tawadros
